on PVP network online biochemical battle mode, an improvement from the original CS's popular biochemical mode. The game features two modes: zombie escape and biochemical infection. In these modes, online players must play as either humans or zombies. Within a limited time frame, humans must either annihilate all zombies or save themselves, while zombies aim to infect all humans through an all-out attack.\n1. Biochemical infection: Within a limited timeframe, humans must eliminate all zombies using firearms or evade them in order to prolong survival, while the zombies actively seek out humans to infect them.\n2. Zombie escape: Within a restricted time frame, humans are required to fend off zombies with firearms for self-preservation and successfully reach the designated endpoint in order to achieve successful escape. The immediate infection of all human players by zombies results in victory.", "short_description": "The first VR Biochemical frenzy online battle in history, Multiplayer shooter in VR with zombies escape, officially opened"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://vrdanceyinsi.webnode.page/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Unity", "support_website_url": "https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1JC4y1n7Uq/?spm_id_from=333.999.0.0&vd_source=f44d7fafb67bf1b4c28885f69f021585", "website_url": "https://renrenren.webnode.page/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "459781504968480"}, {"id": "3744040075834813"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking